  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the heart of our gaming community on Discord and unlock a treasure trove of rewards! Join now and embark on a thrilling journey to score epic loot and dominate the leaderboard. </p></p><br><h1>Free Weekend</h1><p>\"Prepare for adrenaline-pumping action in the skies with Sky Carnage: Aerial Anarchy!<br><br>🚀 Take to the skies in high-speed airplanes.<br>🎯 Unleash devastating firepower on your rivals.<br>🌎 Explore stunning, immersive landscapes.<br>💣 Engage in heart-pounding aerial battles.<br><br>Experience the ultimate airplane racer shooting game that will leave you breathless. Dominate the skies, obliterate your opponents, and become the ultimate flying ace.<br><br>🔥 Join the battle in Sky Carnage: Aerial Anarchy now and rewrite the rules of aerial combat!\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to \"Airplanes Dogfight Racer\", an exciting air racing and battle game where winning is all about conquering the skies! Compete against other airplanes as enemies while completing the race and engaging in intense dogfights. With 5 different weapons to choose from, you can use your machine gun, missiles, mines, shield, and repair kits to emerge victorious.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/411038020af162fc26a4001b63acb71c.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/411038020af162fc26a4001b63acb71c.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/411038020af162fc26a4001b63acb71c.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features alternative routes that offer strategic advantages, making the air race even more thrilling. Choose from three gameplay modes - Championship, Arcade, and Time Trial - and test your skills in solo or multiplayer split-screen modes. The game's difficulty levels, ranging from easy to hard, make it a perfect fit for both novice and expert players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Five Heart-Pounding Race Tracks & 8 High-Flying Airplanes Await!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With five different tracks to unlock, as well as a garage where you can purchase eight different types of airplanes, \"Sky Carnage: Aerial Anarchy\" offers endless hours of entertainment. The unlock system allows you to unlock new items and tracks as you progress, keeping the game fresh and exciting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/def162419c3e9938b1bc374a4c3c47b0.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/def162419c3e9938b1bc374a4c3c47b0.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/def162419c3e9938b1bc374a4c3c47b0.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features Made Easy: Fly Planes, Boosters, Enemies, Weapons, and Local Leaderboards!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's features include an airplane controller, booster cooldown system, enemy AI, and a dogfight system with five weapons. With a local leaderboard, you can compete with your friends and local rivals for the top spot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/cec6d9797b1943a6adc3d88b09f2eebc.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/cec6d9797b1943a6adc3d88b09f2eebc.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/cec6d9797b1943a6adc3d88b09f2eebc.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also includes a countdown system, which adds to the excitement and adrenaline rush. With all these amazing features, \"Sky Carnage: Aerial Anarchy\" is a game that you can't afford to miss. So, what are you waiting for? Download the game now and soar to victory in the skies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to \"Airplanes Dogfight Racer\", an exciting air racing and battle game where winning is all about conquering the skies! Compete against other airplanes as enemies while completing the race and engaging in intense dogfights. With 5 different weapons to choose from, you can use your machine gun, missiles, mines, shield, and repair kits to emerge victorious.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/411038020af162fc26a4001b63acb71c.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/411038020af162fc26a4001b63acb71c.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/411038020af162fc26a4001b63acb71c.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features alternative routes that offer strategic advantages, making the air race even more thrilling. Choose from three gameplay modes - Championship, Arcade, and Time Trial - and test your skills in solo or multiplayer split-screen modes. The game's difficulty levels, ranging from easy to hard, make it a perfect fit for both novice and expert players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Five Heart-Pounding Race Tracks & 8 High-Flying Airplanes Await!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With five different tracks to unlock, as well as a garage where you can purchase eight different types of airplanes, \"Sky Carnage: Aerial Anarchy\" offers endless hours of entertainment. The unlock system allows you to unlock new items and tracks as you progress, keeping the game fresh and exciting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/def162419c3e9938b1bc374a4c3c47b0.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/def162419c3e9938b1bc374a4c3c47b0.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/def162419c3e9938b1bc374a4c3c47b0.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features Made Easy: Fly Planes, Boosters, Enemies, Weapons, and Local Leaderboards!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's features include an airplane controller, booster cooldown system, enemy AI, and a dogfight system with five weapons. With a local leaderboard, you can compete with your friends and local rivals for the top spot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/cec6d9797b1943a6adc3d88b09f2eebc.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/cec6d9797b1943a6adc3d88b09f2eebc.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/cec6d9797b1943a6adc3d88b09f2eebc.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also includes a countdown system, which adds to the excitement and adrenaline rush. With all these amazing features, \"Sky Carnage: Aerial Anarchy\" is a game that you can't afford to miss. So, what are you waiting for? Download the game now and soar to victory in the skies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
